WEBVTT

00:00:00.266 --> 00:00:04.971
The Rater communicates the plan to the Employee on VA Form 750

00:00:05.038 --> 00:00:06.906
at the beginning of the appraisal period,

00:00:06.973 --> 00:00:10.009
usually within 30 days of October 1st.

00:00:10.076 --> 00:00:11.878
The timing is important.

00:00:11.945 --> 00:00:15.148
Employees may only be appraised on elements that apply during

00:00:15.215 --> 00:00:19.252
the current appraisal period, and they need to be aware of them.

00:00:19.319 --> 00:00:23.189
The Employee signs and dates an acknowledgment that he or she

00:00:23.256 --> 00:00:27.193
received the plan, including the performance standards.

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:31.498
Elements and standards will be provided to each Employee annually.

00:00:31.564 --> 00:00:34.601
The Union and Department agree that the Rater should explain

00:00:34.667 --> 00:00:37.604
how the Employee can meet the requirements for a Fully

00:00:37.670 --> 00:00:41.274
Successful and Exceptional rating for each element,

00:00:41.341 --> 00:00:43.676
not only at the beginning of the appraisal period,

00:00:43.743 --> 00:00:45.879
but at any time throughout the period.


